# Information
List of all comics from Marvel to date with python web scraping on comics.org

# How to use the dataset
This dataset can be used for exploratory data analysis

# Column Description
* Series: Series Name
* Year: Published Year
* Issues: Count of issues
* Covers: Count of Covers
* Published: Published Date
* Series Link: The Url of the Series Detail page
* Covers1 Link: The Url of the Covers1 Detail page
* Covers2 Link: The Url of the Covers2 Detail page
